lilgrant_international.Scholarship's Information: Whitworth offers generous academic scholarships to incoming first-year students. There is no scholarship application. Instead, these scholarships are offered to students based on the following criteria: High school weighted GPA and the standardized test score submitted for admission or A-Levels or IB exam scores
